Welcome to Sunfox

Welcome to Sunfox

At Sunfox, we are committed to ensuring that everyone has access to high-quality and affordable medical care. We are pleased to be at the forefront of the medical technology sector and are motivated by a passion for innovation and a dedication to bettering lives.   

At the Foothills of the Himalayas
Building for the Next Billion

At the Foothills of the Himalayas, Building for the Next Billion

Born in the lap of the Himalayas, our R&D lab strives to come up with advanced technologies that can improve healthcare by providing better and more accurate diagnoses, developing more effective treatments, and enhancing patient monitoring. From preventive care and primary healthcare services to life-saving treatments, we are working religiously to ensure that no one is left behind.

Our Journey

2016

Inception

Sunfox Technologies was established as a Research and Development Lab in the Himalayan state of Uttarakhand.

2017

Eureka!

We envisioned the idea of the revolutionary Spandan, and built its first prototype. We also won the Grassroot Innovators Award at IIT Roorkee and started are first office at TBI, GEU.

2018

Appreciations

We were acknowledged and appreciated by the Hon’ble Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi. We also represented India at the World Economic Forum (China).

2019

Levelling Up

We represented India again at the World Economic Forum (China). Taking things forward, we also represented India at the inSpreneur 3.0 Business Summit, Singapore. Ultimately, Spandan was born.

2020

Take Off

We set up a new office at 112, Dharampur, Dehradun. We invigorated the existing Spandan with Spandan 2.0, and were applauded by the National Health Ministry.

2021

Milestone

Had our first ever Angel round and earned seed funding. We were titled as the “Global Winner” for COVID innovation at Extreme Tech Challenge, the world’s largest startup competition. Gradually, our office expanded.

2022

Big Win

Got Featured in Shark Tank Season 1 and procured an all sharks deal from the five maestros, Anupam Mittal, Vineeta Singh, Namita Thapar, Ghazal Alagh and Peyush Bansal.

2023

All the Way Up

Hosted a grand product launch with our dear Shark, Miss Namita Thapar, as the Guest of Honor. We Introduced new portable ECG devices and cutting-edge services aimed at further elevating healthcare worldwide.

Join our Fox Tribe!

Flexible Work Schedule

Building trust through work-life balance and smart work culture where employees work stress-free.

Growing Opportunities

We empower employees to succeed both on the professional and financial front, rewarding great thinking.

Open Culture

Enjoy a workplace that holds interactive sessions to bring different perspectives together.

Novelty Induction

With the novel approach, we push the boundaries of innovation, design, technology, and sustainability.

Foothills of Himalayas

Fortunate to work in Dehradun, a city nestled in the laps of the beautiful Himalayas, we witness amazingly.

Team Work

We work towards a common goal and value the opportunity to learn from the most passionate.

Be a member of an enthusiastic, inventive, and extremely determined team which helps the organisation fulfil its true potential through its hard work and competency. Get a chance to grow with people who challenge convention and defy tradition, bringing forward new ideas and creative techniques to make the world a healthier place.   

If substantial work and a strong work ethic are your priorities, we’ll be glad to have you.

Join Our Fox Tribe
